OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome clear
OL,6,Fintervals in the east this evening,
OL,7,Fbut cloud and rain edging across
OL,8,FCornwall, into parts of Devon, then
OL,9,Fextending east to other areas during
OL,10,Fthe night. Temperatures holding up as
OL,11,Fa result.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FLargely cloudy with a few
OL,14,Fspots of rain during the morning.
OL,15,FGradually brightening up from the west
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon. Becoming quite
OL,17,Fsunny across Cornwall. Feeling cooler
OL,18,Fcompared to Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
